{
  "stem": "25423.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The usual cycle of Jewish holidays, which you'll find in every traditional Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a child, I found the-- [HEBREW]-- I use a Hebrew expression, which means the new years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yom Kippur [INAUDIBLE], rather oppressive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I liked, very much, the [NON-ENGLISH], which means the three pilgrimage holidays-- Passover, Shavu'ot, Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a traditional Saturday at home, which I loved very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As my father was a prominent man and was under continuous pressure of meetings and duties, so it's only on Friday and Saturday that we have-- had him to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the usual.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father used to come from the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as he was orthodox, he used to put, actually, a silk [INAUDIBLE] and a girdle [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And used to pray and sing the welcoming hymns, which are traditional.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had the kiddush.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had little interest in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not only that, as I have pointed out, I had a slight resentment because the pressure's on me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I do other things, which I experienced in the outside world, so I didn't know where I am.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Consequently, I kept relatively neutral-- friendly and neutral.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I liked the Shabbat because of the atmosphere of the house, which was a traditional, cultivated Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was a president of many women's organizations, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the pressures on her were equally great as on my father, because the wife of the rabbi had quite a number of social and-- duties.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The meal consisted, usually, what you would find in every Jewish home in those days-- namely, of gefilte fish, and soup, and meat, and some dessert, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was always a guest.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
